```json
{
  "application": "Gromacs",
  "details": {
    "scheduler": "Slurm",
    "nodes": 4,
    "cores_per_node": 12,
    "threads_per_core": 1,
    "partition": "normal",
    "constraints": "gpu",
    "account": "pr49",
    "software": {
      "gromacs": "/users/revans/programs/gromacs",
      "easybuild": "/users/revans/programs/gromacs/modules/all"
    },
    "environment_variables": {
      "OMP_NUM_THREADS": "$SLURM_CPUS_PER_TASK",
      "CRAY_CUDA_MPS": "1",
      "EASYBUILD_PREFIX": "/users/revans/programs/gromacs",
      "FN": "(cd ..; basename -- "$PWD")",
      "GMX": "gmx"
    },
    "commands": [
      "gmx_mpi mdrun -s md.tpr -ntomp 1 -deffnm md -cpi md.cpt -append -maxh 23.5",
      "cp md.cpt md_${num}.cpt",
      "cp md_prev.cpt md_${num}_prev.cpt",
      "bash CONT.sh",
      "$GMX trjconv -s md.tpr -f md.trr -o md_lastframe.gro -b 500000 -e 500000 -pbc whole",
      "$GMX trjconv -s md.tpr -f md.trr -o ${FN}_protein.gro -b 500000 -e 500000 -pbc whole",
      "$GMX trjconv -s md.tpr -f md.trr -o MD_reimaged.xtc -pbc whole",
      "$GMX trjconv -s min.tpr -f MD_reimaged.xtc -o MD_protraj.xtc -pbc nojump -center",
      "$GMX trjconv -s min.tpr -f MD_protraj.xtc -o MD_cluster.xtc -pbc cluster",
      "$GMX trjconv -s min.tpr -f MD_cluster.xtc -o MD_final.xtc -pbc mol -ur compact -center",
      "$GMX trjconv -s min.tpr -f MD_final.xtc -o ${FN}_protein.pdb -b 500000 -e 500000",
      "$GMX gyrate -s min.tpr -f MD_final.xtc -o ${FN}_Rgyr.xvg",
      "$GMX rms -s min.tpr -f MD_final.xtc -o ${FN}_RMSD.xvg -fit rot+trans"
    ]
  }
}
```
